    "m_ObjectId": "4b4d004fef5e4f3690a8aaa00fabd24d",
    "m_Title": "Vertex shader outputs",
    "m_Content": "These are the endpoints of the per-vertex shader computation. You can also define variables in this block, which are re-used in the pixel shader.",
